儘管前作《運輸大亨》獲得一致好評，但是此遊戲卻未能滿足玩家。大部份評價均為負面的，批評主要集中在[[用户界面|用户界面]]和[[人工智能|人工智能玩家]]上。儘管這些批評均指出此遊戲不及《運輸大亨》，但仍指出有改善之處，如人工智能玩家破壞對手公司車輛的機會被大大地減少。

遊戲評分組織給予此遊戲的分數亦都不太高。兩個匯總評分網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]和[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]分別給予此遊戲59/100分<ref name=Metacritic>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/chris-sawyers-locomotion|title=Chris Sawyer's Locomotion PC|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-02-19}}</ref>和58.89%<ref name=gamerankings2>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/pc/920180-chris-sawyers-locomotion/index.html|title=Chris Sawyer's Locomotion|publisher=[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]|accessdate=2014-02-19}}</ref>。

[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]給予此遊戲6.8/10分，稱讚其策略運用，但就批評遊戲有缺陷。<ref name=GameSpot>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/chris-sawyers-locomotion-review/1900-6108957/|title=Chris Sawyer's Locomotion Review|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2004-09-27|accessdate=2014-02-19}}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]給予此遊戲5.8/10分，並批評遊戲令人沮喪。<ref name=IGN>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/10/06/locomotion-review|title=Locomotion Review|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2004-10-05|accessdate=2014-02-19}}</ref>《[[PCMag|PCMag]]》給予此遊戲3.5/5分，並批評遊戲缺乏挑戰性。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,1713180,00.asp|title=Chris Sawyer's Locomotion|publisher=PCMag|date=|accessdate=2014-02-19}}</ref>[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]給予此遊戲D-評級，並說：「飛機、火車，然後……啊，誰在乎呢？」<ref name=1UP>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/locomotion|title=Chris Sawyer's Locomotion (PC)|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|date=2004-12-15|accessdate=2014-22-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130303171909/http://www.1up.com/reviews/locomotion|archivedate=2013-03-03}}</ref>而[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]則給予此遊戲2/5星，並指出：「運輸大亨的『精神續集』，以去無處快」。<ref name=GameSpy>{{cite web|url=http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/chris-sawyers-locomotion/550170p1.html|title=Chris Sawyer's Locomotion|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|date=2004-09-21|accessdate=2014-22-15}}</ref>

